CREDITS**: I make all our maps and have a number of them. If you like them stop by our server(204.17.65.211:27015). 


DESCRIPTION**: This map takes place in a school. There are a number of hostages to rescue from some in the gym, classrooms, or main offices. You can utilize the roof which works VERY well. All windows are breakable to allow easy access around this large map. As to hold true to all my maps I have randomly included lots of blood and dead bodies. This includes my favorite, the guy being hung in the principals office and the impaled guys in the gym. This is the essence of the [SaltwateR Clan]!
